{"id":"16","parent":"10","text":"Otras: M. xenopi, M. malmoense, M. szulgai, M. simiae, etc. (1)","guid":"rFgz7Riceo4KnUESVjEF5A","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"Patogenia:","guid":"FiJkGNPsk-HhpDonZzRieQ","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Inhalación o ingesta de MNT del ambiente (1)","guid":"h7C9BnuIt7p62R8TzLIuIg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Colonización transitoria en individuos sanos (1)","guid":"VTMk1A7gMnJCbzQIKJSsCw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"Infección en pacientes susceptibles (inmunodeprimidos, daño pulmonar previo) (1)","guid":"Tox7N6w6Ao2IfL7NBQew1Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"a2Q7F0ILsxMxwNYyNMrsdA","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Enfermedad pulmonar: Tos crónica, expectoración, disnea, hemoptisis, fiebre (1)","guid":"75KNYcsVFZtrqG8TwzDL-g","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"Linfadenitis cervical (niños): Aumento indoloro de ganglios, sin respuesta a antibióticos (1)","guid":"BxW1XMvI7nj57zgtHQixeQ","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"Infección diseminada (VIH avanzado): Fiebre, baja de peso, diarrea, anemia (1)","guid":"4RJtI7uNPG3dosojHiB6Ow","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Infecciones de piel y tejidos blandos: Nódulos, abscesos, úlceras (1)","guid":"ffancDVJaTX1yc6UMT_gkA","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"Estudio:","guid":"8Tk-mA25tmwaLdJU6PLaDg","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Baciloscopía y cultivo de Koch de expectoración, lavado broncoalveolar o biopsia (1)","guid":"e7mdBbU562UgX-LXeijvQg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Radiografía y TAC de tórax: Bronquiectasias, nódulos, cavidades (1)","guid":"XFgtXXHNJ8I0OuSTM5U8Qw","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"Identificación de especie por pruebas bioquímicas, cromatográficas o moleculares (1)","guid":"MyfApWz58_PsybplnfaDsw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"Susceptibi